[33mtag v1.0.0-beta[m
Tagger: josevilanir <vilanirneto@hotmail.com>
Date:   Fri Feb 20 14:37:15 2026 -0300

Release v1.0.0-beta - Versao Beta Inicial

Primeira versao beta funcional do Comic Creator.

Features principais:
- Clean Architecture completa
- API REST com documentacao
- Frontend React moderno
- Download e organizacao de mangas
- Geracao de PDFs e thumbnails
- Testes automatizados

Stack: Python 3.12, Flask, React 18, SQLite

Data: 20/02/2026

